lyTime":"2017-02-04T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"你想點？咪死背囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀過 physio / anatomy / mi bio / food mi bio / cell bio"},{"pid":"66217b4e916d829f8716c4e9c460103ba0ab0830","tid":107410,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38842ee09f579635d5ecbdc2f9b317773497404e","tid":107410,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拜柯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入黎都打算咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3505ddb1c967ef57bf81988780f4fe0703d35913","tid":107410,"uid":24477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"好現實<br />\n就算理解完都唔一定exam考得好<br />\n有時要食下書/notes"},{"pid":"136b638228bf896f6e13ae18a8fb3c6b4e2fc49a","tid":107410,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07de61dc94de58b7103754a22e7b2318b2df9efc","tid":107410,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"大學要讀bio 中學冇修bio 好彩sem1都叫生存到"},{"pid":"a36feb337a3ad3379e0fad0765413f26fec55494","tid":107410,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e3d151df0b0a76f7a83211bbb87be27b8ef3d6a","tid":107410,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcdd6b459b24bbb361bf95c44c2495eb503ca239","tid":107410,"uid":56276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大學要讀bio 中學冇修bio 好彩sem1都叫生存到</blockquote><br />\nscience 狗</blockquote><br />\n你個名改得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n又係你個亂屌人既痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f1475f8c73a537421784db209c4f1ed730873c","tid":107410,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22f944df0d61d76da547d4f5d5e57766af459d6a","tid":107410,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"我無bio 底又覺得ok<br />\n最緊要好記性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd569d085292135ae2618967d2e341e66b514ed","tid":107410,"uid":75954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"鳩背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我都覺得有咩技巧<br />\n不過當我問下讀醫啲人點背，佢地都係話係咁背嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只好係咁背<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身背野唔叻，中學又冇讀過bio，之前都係好差<br />\n我覺得首先明哂大部分d medical prefix suffix先，之後再讀就會輕鬆好多<br />\n雖然廢話，但花得越多時間記憶會越穩固<br />\n同埋越習慣記野，記野能力會越黎越好<br />\n如果一個sem幾科bio我就會不斷take turn咁溫<br />\nE.g A,B,C 3科，3個鐘我會溫1個鐘each而唔係3個鐘其中一科，一來可以每科都至少有啲印象，二來我自己會冇咁悶<br />\n好似有研究話分開記同一樣野n次(e.g 12次5分鐘each)好過一次過花(1個鐘)落同一樣野 (sorry冇source)<br />\n利申: related major final year讀過micbio/human bio/Anat/physio/patho etc"}]}